{"tid":1933240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Not Huawei]【獨有功能】SmarTone：選用Ericsson 5G頻譜","createTime":"2020-03-19T07:33:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T18:51:58.000Z","uid":51271,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6448fdde0bbcffa7a041a39f875c3176ada932","tid":1933240,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:33:06.000Z","msg":"SmarTone（0315）宣布，將採用愛立信（Ericsson）5G獨有的頻譜共享功能，愛立信亦會為SmarTone建構無線接入網 （RAN） 及核心網，未來五年內雙方將合作推動本地5G服務，合作範疇包括雙模5G雲端核網的應用，全面網路功能虛擬化、人工智能驅動的無線接入等。本地另外兩間電訊商，香港電訊（6823）及和記電訊（0215）早前已宣布會與華為合作發展5G網絡。<br />\n<br />\nSmarTone科技總裁鄒金根表示，一直與愛立信攜手積極迎接5G時代，並早於兩年前在香港共同進行首個5G技術展示，與愛立信致力帶領流動通訊設備的技術發展，並共同於多個測試、研究和產品開發中領導業界。愛立信則指出，一直重視網絡安全及於此範疇上具領導地位，多年來投放大量資源建立安全的網絡基建並將其標準化，並將採用「安全及可靠性模型」，著重跨無線網絡基建、核心網、雲端基建的設計。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1584601753557&amp;issue=20200319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1584601753557%26issue%3D20200319&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFT632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=7bb6ee27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1584601753557&amp;issue=20200319</a>"},{"pid":"528b5c37d0337b263aa76900ddfface4044a5223","tid":1933240,"uid":52605,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:35:15.000Z","msg":"建議重要事唔好打電話<br />\n因為電話機樓都係華為設備"},{"pid":"4c76be1e6551791da8acf33f8076925ceb838686","tid":1933240,"uid":49329,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:53:53.000Z","msg":"smart tone 用户揮手區！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa25b026f147afcc22e9a418c47c399c206dfe3","tid":1933240,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:54:17.000Z","msg":"Wow"},{"pid":"2db12de74b1851add1f92